Package icyllis.modernui.text

Class PrecomputedText.Params

java.lang.Object
icyllis.modernui.text.PrecomputedText.Params
Enclosing class:
PrecomputedText
public static final class PrecomputedText.Params extends Object
The information required for building PrecomputedText.

Contains information required for precomputing text measurement metadata, so it can be done in isolation of a TextView or StaticLayout, when final layout constraints are not known.
